<item>
<title>[SJN-18] NumberConverter needs to know what type was desired</title>
<link>http://issues.osjava.org/jira/browse/SJN-18</link>

                    <description>The NumberConverter links to java.lang.Number. If it knew exactly what type was wanted, it could try harder.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
To this end, Converters need to be told what type they are dealing with. That way a DateConverter could also handle java.sql.Date etc.</description>
